OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls despite
OL,4,Ceasing inflation
OL,6,FConsumer confidence has fallen in a
OL,7,Fblow for retailers as customers veer
OL,8,Faway from big-ticket purchases,
OL,9,Ffigures show.
OL,11,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,12,FIndex dropped three points to minus 19
OL,13,Fin February to a level last seen in
OL,14,FNovember, despite easing inflation.
OL,16,FThe decline was mainly driven by
OL,17,Fweaker perceptions of personal
OL,18,Ffinances ` looking back over the last
OL,19,Fyear and ahead to the next 12 months `
OL,20,Fwhich both fell by four points.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
