OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772175649
OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls despite
OL,4,Ceasing inflation
OL,6,FThe major purchase index ` an
OL,7,Findicator of confidence in buying big-
OL,8,Fticket items ` also fell by four
OL,9,Fpoints, to minus 14.
OL,11,FExpectations for the general economy
OL,12,Fover the next 12 months remained
OL,13,Funchanged at minus 31 ` the same as
OL,14,Fthe score a year ago.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, a measure of confidence in
OL,17,Fsaving money, which is part of the
OL,18,Fsurvey but does not contribute to the
OL,19,Foverall score, fell seven points to 21
OL,20,F` nine points lower than last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
