OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772175649
OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls despite
OL,4,Ceasing inflation
OL,6,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,7,Fdirector at GfK, said: "Fewer people
OL,8,Fsay that now is a good time to make
OL,9,Fmajor purchases and fewer consumers
OL,10,Fintend to save money.
OL,12,F"Although the rate of inflation is
OL,13,Feasing, prices continue to rise,
OL,14,Fforcing many households to prioritise
OL,15,Fday-to-day spending over longer-term
OL,16,Fneeds.
OL,18,F"Views on the broader economy remain
OL,19,Ffirmly in negative territory, with
OL,20,Fconsumers anticipating only limited
OL,21,Feconomic growth this year.
