OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772175649
OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls despite
OL,4,Ceasing inflation
OL,6,F"Unemployment has now reached its
OL,7,Fhighest level in nearly five years,
OL,8,Fand this is increasing concerns about
OL,9,Fjob security, particularly given the
OL,10,Fbackdrop of weak wage growth. With
OL,11,Ffewer entry-level opportunities
OL,12,Favailable, those on lower incomes are
OL,13,Falready feeling the strain, and this
OL,14,Ftrend risks undermining the typically
OL,15,Fmore optimistic outlook held by
OL,16,Fyounger age groups."
